<h3>4.3.4 Product Customization (Variants)</h3>
<p>The single product details page replaces a standard "buy button" with an interactive variant calculator. As users independently manipulate dropdown selectors designating cake sizes, distinct flavors, or structural shapes, React states mathematically apply additive logic rendering accurate subtotal metrics globally confirming exact prices prior to cart population.</p>
