<h3>4.3.5 Cart, Checkout, and Payment</h3>
<p>The Checkout pipeline functions across conditional rendering loops. Altering payment preferences actively mutates subsequent form requirements. Selecting 'Online Payments' forces 100% full transaction logs; however, choosing 'Cash On Delivery' automatically renders visual warnings establishing a mandatory 30% advance deposit barrier organically. Further, checkout integrates a Loyalty Redemption slider actively validating applied points securely capping discounts exclusively below 30% totals systematically.</p>
